<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') -%>
<div class="container min-h-screen mt-12">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 px-8 pt-20">
    <div class="px-6 py-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md text-center md:mt-0">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Your One-Stop Destination</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        I-Mart shopping store is your one-stop destination for all your online
        shopping needs. With a diverse range of products from top-rated sellers,
        we ensure that you find exactly what you're looking for.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Whether you're searching for fashion, electronics, home goods, or
        accessories, we've got it all covered. Our platform offers a seamless
        shopping experience with secure transactions and reliable sellers,
        giving you peace of mind every time you shop.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="px-6 py-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md text-center mt-8 md:mt-0"
    >
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Wide Range of Products</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        From fashion to electronics, home goods to accessories, we've got it all
        covered. Our platform offers a diverse range of products to cater to
        your every need. Whether you're looking for the latest trends or
        everyday essentials, you'll find them all here.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        With secure transactions and reliable sellers, you can shop with
        confidence on I-Mart shopping store. Join our community today and
        experience the convenience of online shopping like never before!
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="px-6 py-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md text-center mt-8 md:mt-0"
    >
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Join Our Community</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Join our growing community of shoppers and sellers today! Whether you're
        a buyer looking for the best deals or a seller wanting to reach a wider
        audience, I-MART shopping store is the perfect platform for you.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        With easy navigation, secure transactions, and reliable customer
        support, we ensure a hassle-free shopping experience for all our users.
        Join us now and be a part of the future of online shopping!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12 px-8 mb-12">
    <div class="shadow-md p-8 rounded-lg" id="contact-us">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Have any questions or concerns? Feel free to contact us using the form
        below. We'll get back to you as soon as possible.
      </p>
      <form action="" method="">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <label for="email" class="block text-lg mb-2">Email:</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            class="w-full px-2 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-400"
            required
          />
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <label for="message" class="block text-lg mb-2">Message:</label>
          <textarea
            id="message"
            name="message"
            rows="5"
            class="w-full px-2 py-2 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-400"
            required
          ></textarea>
        </div>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition duration-300"
        >
          Submit
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="shadow-md p-8 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Terms and Conditions</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-4">
        <li class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-2">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
